otball in Argentina|Argentine football]]. The season covers the period from 1 July 2017 to 30 June 2018.\n\n==Current squad==\n{{Updated|7 September 2017}}.<ref name=\"Soccerway profile\">{{cite news|title=Lan\u00fas squad|url=https://int.soccerway.com/teams/argentina/ca-lanus/101/squad/|accessdate=15 August 2017|work=Soccerway|date=15 August 2017}}</ref>\n\n{{Fs start}}<!--start of 1st column for table-->\n{{Fs player|no=1 |nat=ARG|pos=GK|name=[[Fernando Monetti]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=2 |nat=ARG|pos=DF|name=[[Marcelo Herrera (footballer, born 1992)|Marcelo Herrera]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=3 |nat=ARG|pos=DF|name=[[Maximiliano Vel\u00e1zquez]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=4 |nat=ARG|pos=DF|name=[[Jos\u00e9 Luis G\u00f3mez (footballer)|Jos\u00e9 G\u00f3mez]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=6 |nat=ARG|pos=DF|name=[[Diego Braghieri]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=7 |nat=ARG|pos=FW|name=[[Lautaro Acosta]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=8 |nat=ARG|pos=MF|name=[[Fernando Barrientos]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=9 |nat=ARG|pos=FW|name=[[Jos\u00e9 Sand]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=16|nat=URU|pos=FW|name=[[Alejandro Silva Gonz\u00e1lez|Alejandro Silva]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=17|nat=ARG|pos=FW|name=[[Germ\u00e1n Denis]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=19|nat=ARG|pos=MF|name=[[Nicol\u00e1s Aguirre (footballer)|Nicol\u00e1s Aguirre]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=21|nat=ARG|pos=MF|name=[[Nicol\u00e1s Pasquini]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=22|nat=ARG|pos=DF|name=[[Santiago Zurbriggen]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=23|nat=PAR|pos=DF|name=[[Rolando Garc\u00eda (Paraguayan footballer)|Rolando Garc\u00eda]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=24|nat=ARG|pos=MF|name=[[Leandro Maciel]]}}\n{{Fs mid}}<!--start of 2nd column for table-->\n{{Fs player|no=25|nat=ARG|pos=FW|name=[[Marcelino Moreno]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=27|nat=ARG|pos=MF|name=[[Rom\u00e1n Mart\u00ednez (footballer)|Rom\u00e1n Mart\u00ednez]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=28|nat=ARG|pos=GK|name=Nicol\u00e1s Avellaneda}}\n{{Fs player|no=30|nat=ARG|pos=MF|name=[[Iv\u00e1n Marcone]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=31|nat=ARG|pos=GK|name=[[Esteban Andrada]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=33|nat=ARG|pos=DF|name=[[G