om ''[[Game of Thrones]]'')<ref name= \"feud\">{{cite news |last=Truitt |first=Brian |url= https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/entertainthis/2019/05/05/snl-pits-avengers-vs-game-thrones-hilarious-family-feud/1107698001/ |title=''SNL' pits 'Avengers: Endgame' vs. 'Game of Thrones' on hilarious 'Family Feud' |work=[[USA Today]] |date=May 5, 2019 |accessdate=May 6, 2019}}</ref>\n* [[Ana Navarro]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Wfl-uMVbNn8|title=The View: Jenny McCarthy on Vaccines {{endash}} SNL | date=April 4, 2019|publisher=[[Saturday Night Live]]|via=[[YouTube]]|accessdate=January 24, 2020}}</ref>\n{{colend}}\n\n==Filmography==\n=== Film ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! class=\"unsortable\"| Notes\n! Ref.\n|-\n| 2010\n| ''[[The 41-Year-Old Virgin Who Knocked Up Sarah Marshall and Felt Superbad About It|The 41-Year-Old Virgin Who Knocked Up <br/>Sarah Marshall and Felt Superbad About It]]''\n| Sara\n|\n|<ref name=Jones20160912>{{Cite web |url=https://www.cinemablend.com/television/1555292/snl-just-added-two-more-brand-new-cast-members |title=SNL Just Added Two More Brand New Cast Members |last=Jones |first=Adrienne |date=September 12, 2016 |website=Cinema Blend |access-date=November 24, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2016\n| ''[[Laid in America]]''\n| Ms. Hopkins\n|\n|<ref name=Andrews20160913 />\n|-\n| 2018\n| ''[[Ralph Breaks the Internet]]''\n| Taffyta Muttonfudge (voice)\n| Replaces [[Mindy Kaling]]\n|<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2018/11/ralph-breaks-the-internet-cast |title=Ralph Breaks the Internet's Cast List Is Full of Fun, Surprising Easter Eggs |last=Desta |first=Yohana |date=November 21, 2018 |website=[[Vanity Fair (magazine)|Vanity Fair]] |access-date=November 24, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''[[Toy Story 4]]''\n| Karen Beverly (voice)\n|\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2019/film/reviews/toy-story-4-review-1203241658/|title=Film Review: 'Toy Story 4'|last =DeBruge|first =Peter|work