m)|Korn]]''\n* Korpse - ''Pull the Flood''\n* [[Kyuss]] \u2013 ''[[Welcome to Sky Valley]]''\n* [[Lake of Tears]] \u2013 ''[[Greater Art]]''\n* Luciferion - ''Demonication (The Manifest)''\n* [[Tony MacAlpine]] \u2013 ''[[Premonition (Tony MacAlpine album)|Premonition]]''\n* [[Machine Head (band)|Machine Head]] \u2013 ''[[Burn My Eyes]]''\n* [[Madball]] \u2013 ''Set It Off''\n* [[Magnum (band)|Magnum]] \u2013 ''[[Rock Art (album)|Rock Art]]''\n* [[Yngwie Malmsteen]] \u2013 ''[[The Seventh Sign (album)|The Seventh Sign]]''\n* [[Marduk (band)|Marduk]] \u2013 ''[[Opus Nocturne]]''\n* [[Marilyn Manson (band)|Marilyn Manson]] \u2013 ''[[Portrait of an American Family]]''\n* [[Mayhem (band)|Mayhem]] \u2013 ''[[De Mysteriis Dom Sathanas]]''\n* [[Megadeth]] \u2013 ''[[Youthanasia]]''\n* [[Melvins]] \u2013 ''[[Stoner Witch]]''\n* [[Memento Mori]] \u2013 ''[[Life, Death, and Other Morbid Tales]]''\n* [[Mercyful Fate]] \u2013 ''[[Time (Mercyful Fate album)|Time]]''\n* [[Moonspell]] \u2013 ''[[Under the Moonspell]]'' (EP)\n* [[Mortification (band)|Mortification]] - ''[[Blood World]]''\n* [[M\u00f6tley Cr\u00fce]] \u2013 ''[[M\u00f6tley Cr\u00fce (album)|M\u00f6tley Cr\u00fce]]''\n* [[My Dying Bride]] - ''[[I Am the Bloody Earth]]'' (EP)\n* [[Nailbomb]] \u2013 ''[[Point Blank (Nailbomb album)|Point Blank]]''\n* [[Napalm Death]] \u2013 ''[[Fear, Emptiness, Despair]]''\n* [[Nine Inch Nails]] \u2013 ''[[The Downward Spiral]]''\n* [[No One Is Innocent]] \u2013 ''[[No One Is Innocent]]''\n* [[Legion of the Damned (band)|Occult]] \u2013 ''Prepare to Meet Thy Doom''\n* [[Obituary (band)|Obituary]] \u2013 ''[[World Demise]]''\n* [[The Obsessed]] \u2013 ''[[The Church Within]]''\n* [[Oomph!]] \u2013 ''[[Sperm (album)|Sperm]]''\n* [[Overkill (band)|Overkill]] \u2013 ''[[W.F.O.]]''\n* [[Pantera]] \u2013 ''[[Far Beyond Driven]]''\n* [[Pearl Jam]] \u2013 ''[[Vitalogy]]''\n* [[Pitchshifter (band)|Pitchshifter]] \u2013 ''[[The Remix War]]'' (remix)\n* [[Pro-Pain]] \u2013 ''The Truth Hurts''\n*